flowchart TD
    A[Start Episode<br/>role=folder/disturber] --> B[Main Control Loop]
    B --> B0{Ctrl+Space pressed?}
    B0 -->|Yes| S[Enter human takeover mode]
    B0 -->|No| C{Stop / exit_early?}
    C -->|Yes| Z[End Episode Loop]
    C -->|No| D{No time limit<br/>max_time_s=null}

    D --> E[Get observation + check home]

    E --> F{At home, all joints within threshold=2.5<br/>all joint speeds below speed_threshold=0.5<br/>and not already evaluated in this home stay?}
    F -->|No| H[Continue action branch]
    F -->|Yes| F1{home_wait_s=2.0 elapsed?}
    F1 -->|No| F2[Keep inference running<br/>If leave home: reset timer]
    F2 --> H
    F1 -->|Yes| G[Home-only success: no value model needed]

    G --> K1[task_success=True<br/>end_reason=home_success<br/>End loop immediately]

    H --> L[No collision detection<br/>no safety config for fold cloth]
    L --> M[Policy/teleop action execution]

    S --> T{Ctrl+Space to exit takeover?}
    T -->|No| S
    T -->|Yes| V0[Exit takeover<br/>resume inference]
    V0 --> B
    M --> M1{Inference timeout?}
    M1 -->|Yes| S
    M1 -->|No| B

    Z --> ZA[Label success/fail by home status]
    ZA --> ZB{At home?}
    ZB -->|No| ZH[Call for human takeover<br/>move robot back home]
    ZH --> ZB
    ZB -->|Yes| ZC[Wait home stable]
    ZC --> ZD[Advance role: folder↔disturber]
    ZD --> ZE[Next episode]

    style G fill:#90EE90
    style K1 fill:#90EE90
    style L fill:#FFE4B5
